0;147;0RUNdef ciferny_soucet(n):\n    sum = 0\n    while n != 0:\n        rest = n % 10\n        sum += rest\n        n = (n - rest) / 10\n    return sum\nTESTprint ciferny_soucet(8429) 
1;2;1SUBMITdef ciferny_soucet(n):\n    sum = 0\n    while n != 0:\n        rest = n % 10\n        sum += rest\n        n = (n - rest) / 10\n    return sum\n

0;68;0RUNdef ciferny_soucet(n):\n    i = 10\n    f = 0\n    cif = []\n    while True:\n        n -= f\n        f = n%i\n        cif.append(f/(i/10))\n        if i>n:\n            break\n        i*=10\n    return sum(cif)\nTESTprint ciferny_soucet

0;85;0RUNdef ciferny_soucet(n):\n    soucet = 0\n    cifra = 0\n    while n != 0:\n    cifra = n % 10\n        n -= cifra\n        n /= 10\n    return soucet\nTESTprint ciferny_soucet(7491)
